          <Base:Description type="brief">
             black steel and knotty walnut snaphaunce musket
          </Base:Description>
          <Base:Description type="examine">
             This black steel and knotty walnut snaphaunce musket is an expertly crafted custom design. It has a long, sleek steel barrel and a sturdy stock that has been crafted from knotty black walnut, the butt plate made from an ivory myr horn. This is a weapon involving wound springs and gunpowder which can fire a bullet with great force. {? | $(this.firearm:loaded) | The musket is loaded. }
          </Base:Description>
          <Base:Description type="look">
             A black steel and knotty walnut snaphaunce musket with a long, sleek steel barrel. The sturdy stock is crafted from knotty black walnut, the butt plate made from an ivory myr horn. {? | $(this.firearm:loaded) | The musket is loaded. }
